lead_paragraph: Big money signings and investments in storied European clubs, and the backing of a president who is an avid soccer fan: things should be looking up for millions of Chinese supporting the 'beautiful game'.

headline.print_headline: In China's Quest to Conquer World Soccer, Fans Feel Left Behind
headline.main: In China's Quest to Conquer World Soccer, Fans Feel Left Behind
